title: गुज्जरों के प्रदर्शन का पुराना वीडियो कश्मीर में पुलिस द्वारा मुसलमानों को पीटने के गलत दावे से साझा
author: www.altnews.in
vclaim: WATCH | A large number of people belonging to the Gujjar community today held protest outside Jammu and Kashmir Forest Minister Chaudhary Lal Singh’s residence in Jammu against eviction of people, especially members of their tribe, from forest belts. pic.twitter.com/qwODQ47VUf
